title: 815. Which Second-Year QBs Will Make the Biggest Leap?
itunes:title: 815. Which Second-Year QBs Will Make the Biggest Leap?
description:
Rhett Lewis and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys react to the news of Buccaneers quarterback Tom Brady's massive deal to join FOX Sports as an analyst after his playing career. Then, the pair discuss which second-year quarterbacks will make the biggest leap in 2022. To wrap up the show, the duo pick which other second-year players are poised to take a leap.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
